<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Verification - uVision</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px;
        }
        .otp-container {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .otp-code {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #667eea;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
        .warning {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            color: #856404;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .security-tips {
            background: #e7f3ff;
            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .security-tips h4 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #0c5460;
        }
        .security-tips ul {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üìß Email Verification</h1>
            <p>Welcome to uVision!</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Verify Your Email Address</h2>
            <p>Thank you for joining uVision! To complete your registration and secure your account, please verify your email address.</p>
            
            <div class="otp-container">
                <h3>Your Verification Code</h3>
                <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
                <p><small>Enter this code to verify your email address</small></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="warning">
                <strong>‚è∞ This code will expire in 10 minutes</strong><br>
                If you don't verify within this time, you'll need to request a new code.
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-tips">
                <h4>üîí Security Tips</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Never share this verification code with anyone</li>
                    <li>uVision will never ask for your code via phone or email</li>
                    <li>If you didn't create an account, you can safely ignore this email</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p>Once verified, you'll be able to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Access your uVision account</li>
                <li>Connect with creative professionals</li>
                <li>Manage your bookings and projects</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>If you have any questions or need help, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>uVision</strong> - Connecting You with Creative Professionals</p>
            <p>üìß support@uvision.com | üìû +1 (555) 123-4567</p>
            <p><small>This is an automated email. Please do not reply to this email address.</small></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
